title: Manziel, Dez Bryant & rookie whispers
itunes:title: Manziel, Dez Bryant & rookie whispers
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- react to the latest NFL news on Johnny Manziel's growth (7:10), Dez Bryant's contract situation (11:38) and the Packers offensive fire power (27:21). The guys then reveal the latest rookie whispers surrounding Jameis Winston, Marcus Mariota, Amari Cooper and much more (32:31).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
